summary: A retexture of the Dining Set.
descriptionHtml:
Dining Set Complete Retexture

RECOMMENDED FILES TO USE WITH THIS:
HeadBomb\'s Forksassin mod - [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4745]Forksassin mod[/url]

Replaces the current low res textures of these items. For those of you who have found the wield-able versions of the Knife and Fork this is for you. Who wouldn\'t want to kill a dragon with eating utensils?

Instructions:
Simply drag/drop the \"Data\" folder into your \"Skyrim\" folder

Credits:

Textures by -Rusty- aka RustyZombie01

Models by Bethesda
